MAIN_MESSAGE: There is power cut in the DG9 postcode area of Stranraer. We had no advance warning of this and only became aware of it at 3:58pm. Our emergency response team have now arrived on site. Our team will work to get your power back on as quickly and as safely as possible by 6:00pm. We apologise for the inconvenience and thank you for your patience. This message was updated at 5:20pm on Monday, 04 January 2021
